# cortex/ Directory Structure. Compilers, runtimes, and interpreters for programming languages.

```
cortex/
├── .template/        # Template for new language directories
├── .utils/           # Utility scripts
├── .base/            # Base container configurations
├── [language]/       # Language-specific hello world examples
│   ├── Dockerfile    # Container definition
│   ├── Makefile      # Build instructions
│   ├── README.md     # Language-specific documentation
│   ├── artifacts/    # Build artifacts
│   └── files/        # Source code files
└── Makefile          # Main build system
```

## Indexing Guidelines

Only index programming languages that are human-comprehensible. Exclude esoteric languages like:
- brainfuck
- befunge
- unlambda
- whitespace
- lolcode
- emojicode
- arnoldc

These languages are primarily designed as programming puzzles rather than practical tools for human communication and should be excluded from indexing and analysis.